      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so quiet lately. like, i sit here in this apartment all day, i do my work, i log on, i log off... and it feels like i'm just a ghost. if i didn't show up to the zoom calls tomorrow, would anyone even actually notice? or would they just think my internet was down for a bit?",
